celled\\|refunded |\n| `StockRecord` | inventory/repository | Available and reserved stock |\n| `PriceBreakdown` | billing/calculator | Itemized price calculation |\n| `PaymentRecord` | billing/service | Payment transaction record |\n| `NotificationRecord` | notifications/service | Sent notification log entry |\n\n---\n\n### 10. BUILD & TEST CONFIGURATION\n\n**Package.json Scripts:**\n- `npm run build` - Compiles TypeScript (tsc)\n- `npm run lint` - ESLint checks\n- `npm test` - Vitest runs all tests\n\n**TypeScript Config:**\n- Target: ES2022\n- Module: Node16 (ESM)\n- Strict mode: enabled\n- Output: ./dist\n- Source: ./src\n\n**Total Test Count:** 30 visible tests across 5 test files\n\n---\n\nThis is a well-structured event-driven system with clear separation of concerns, using a pub/sub event bus to decouple order, inventory, billing, and notification services."}],"totalDurationMs":40825,"totalTokens":31907,"totalToolUseCount":22,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":974,"cache_read_input_tokens":27373,"output_tokens":3556,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":974,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[]}}}
